Lots of good stuff packed away in all that text. Unfortunately it will not be seen and heard by anyone from verant on these message boards. <P>The official sony boards at <A HREF="http://www.everquest.com" TARGET=_blank>www.everquest.com</A>  is where you should post this.<P>Tomething you said triggered a thought. We could summon weapons to give to our pets and Necro's couldnt. They made 39th level pets auto dual wield and told us it was a fix for our class. In reality it was a candy for the necro's only.. the favored class (well druids too).
